"{\"uid\": \"duluthnewstribune.com-lifestyle-dave-hoops-column-judging-olympics-of-beer-no-easy-feat\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sponsored By  ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT  Greetings, my friends.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 81, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, I am writing about the most major beer competition for beer - not necessarily award-winning beer, but the process and the significance of producing an award-winning beer.\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a fun topic, and I love the idea of trying to explain it.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  I write this after returning from judging the World Beer Cup in Las Vegas.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.7201485018536423, \"rank\": 0.3885901998782442, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This yearly event takes place just before the Craft Brewers Conference, the yearly conference and trade show for the brewing industry.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is often called \\\"the Olympics of Beer\\\" and began in 1996.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each year, these two events take place in a different city.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year was Nashville; it was in Las Vegas for the first time.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"score\": 0.9903687489622235, \"rank\": 0.009722260103641661, \"text\": \"Nashville\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\"}, {\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.7201485018536423, \"rank\": 0.3885901998782442, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This competition is one of the largest in the world and is unique in that the beers are also from all over the world.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The numbers are impressive: 290 judges from 37 countries spent seven days judging 9,300 beers over 110 categories.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's over 60,000 bottles and cans opened and served by over 300 hardworking volunteers.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was impressed this year with the high quality of most beers I tried.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The judges are very committed and serious about their jobs.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We taste all day, get there early, and keep focus.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Becoming a judge is a rigorous path that requires many steps and expertise.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was told the waiting list is currently three years long and many of the folks I worked with this year had 10-25 years under their belts, so new blood gets added slowly as the competition grows.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  I am going to explain how we go about judging these beers.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's the process?\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To enter a medal-worthy beer, the brewer puts huge energy into the recipe and the process and thoughtfully considers the category.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, the safe transport of the beer to the judging venue is critical.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The actual judging is blind.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not know who made the sample we are evaluating.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are given a category to judge, for example, American Pale Ale.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usually, six judges at a table will judge by rounds.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first round will typically have 12 beers and we judges pick the three best beers to advance to the next round.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do this by evaluating the beer on several attributes: appearance, aroma, flavor and taste, mouthfeel, technical achievement, true to style, and overall impression.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We note comments for the brewer to receive after the competition.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When a beer advances to Round 2, the process repeats.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To win a medal, three to five rounds must usually be \\\"won\\\" to advance.\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  At the end, medals are awarded based on these criteria:  I am in a unique situation because I am a national-level judge and participate in the process of awarding medals, but I have also been submitting beers in competitions for many years.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, I am not allowed to judge any categories in which I have entered a beer.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, again, it's a unique perspective of being invested in both sides of the process.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This adds to a great perspective in the discussion.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But what does it all mean?\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means winning breweries can advertise their success verified by experts to the public.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that their beer stands out in excellence.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that breweries are willing to submit beer with subjective judging in a hugely competitive environment where many great beers are passed up.\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are the competitions fair?\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before I started as an official judge, I often felt no, they were not (if I did not win).\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, I feel strongly that they are very fair and are being judged by many of the very best beer evaluators on the planet.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not trying to say only seek out medal-winning beer.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No way.\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Always enjoy the beers you love.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But breweries that do have distinctive awards in their quiver are surely worth a try.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT    Hopefully, I have helped those of you interested in the \\\"how\\\" of beer competitions and given you some ideas to seek out.\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The results of the 2024 World Beer Cup are atworldbeercup.org.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for reading and please email me with questions or comments.\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dave Hoops, who lives and works in Duluth, is a veteran brewer and beer judge.\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4048, \"end\": 4054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota_Duluth\", \"score\": 0.9941787619287776, \"rank\": 0.005854980522508149, \"text\": \"Duluth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota_Duluth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota_Duluth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a beer-related question for Dave?\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Email him atdave@hoopsbrewing.comor the News Tribune atlifestyle@duluthnews.com.\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4243, \"entities\": []}]}"